---
import SplitLayout from '../layouts/SplitLayout.astro';
const title = "Kindle Jailbreak Guide";
---

<SplitLayout title={title}>
  <h2>Kindle Jailbreak Guide</h2>
  <p>The Amazon Kindle is one of the most popular e-readers worldwide, but it has limitations like restricted file formats, no third-party apps, and limited customization.</p>

  <h3>Supported Kindle Models</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Kindle Paperwhite (1st to latest generation)</li>
    <li>Kindle Oasis (all versions)</li>
    <li>Kindle Basic (various models)</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Why Jailbreak Your Kindle?</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Install custom reading apps such as KOReader for advanced features</li>
    <li>Customize fonts, margins, and UI themes beyond Amazon’s defaults</li>
    <li>Read unsupported e-book formats (ePub, etc.)</li>
    <li>Access enhanced annotations and note-taking features</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Step-by-Step Jailbreak Process</h3>
  <ol>
    <li><strong>Check your Kindle firmware:</strong> Go to Settings &gt; Device Info and note the firmware version.</li>
    <li><strong>Find the correct jailbreak tool:</strong> Each firmware may require a specific jailbreak method. Popular tools are “Kindle Jailbreak” scripts maintained by the community.</li>
    <li><strong>Download the jailbreak files:</strong> Use trusted sources like MobileRead forums.</li>
    <li><strong>Connect your Kindle to your PC:</strong> via USB cable and transfer jailbreak files.</li>
    <li><strong>Run the jailbreak script:</strong> Follow exact instructions for your model and firmware.</li>
    <li><strong>Install KOReader:</strong> After jailbreaking, KOReader can be installed to enhance your reading experience.</li>
  </ol>

  <h3>Safety Tips</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Backup all important files and settings before proceeding</li>
    <li>Do not interrupt the process or disconnect during the jailbreak</li>
    <li>Use verified, community-trusted tools only</li>
    <li>Be aware that firmware updates from Amazon may undo your jailbreak</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Further Resources</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.mobileread.com/forums/forumdisplay.php?f=142" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MobileRead Kindle Jailbreak Forum</a></li>
    <li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLkindleyouneed" target="_blank" rel="noopener">YouTube Tutorials</a></li>
  </ul>
</SplitLayout>
